11.Bd2  h6  
12.a4  { Grabbing space on the queenside. } c6  
13.c3  dxc3  
14.Bxc3  {[%cal Ba4a5]} {[%cal Bf1e1]} {[%cal Bh2h3]} {[%cal Bd1b3]} ( 14. Bxc3 { With an easy-to-play position. Next, we can play a prophylactic } 14...-- 15.h3 { , increase pressure on the f7-pawn by playing } 15...-- 16.Qb3 { and expand on the queenside with } 16...-- 17.a5 { . } )  *

