5.Bc4  {[%csl Rf7]} {[%cal Bc4f7]} ( { The line after } 5.d4?! exd4 6.Nxd4 Bg7 { doesn't work because Black's setup suddenly makes a lot of sense. Apparently, we just helped Black to activate his dark-squared bishop and justified his whole idea. } ) Bg7  
6.d3  ( 6. d3 { Our idea here is to delay castling and make other useful moves instead. In some cases we will push } 6...-- 7.h4 { , } -- 8.h5! ) d6  
