{ In this chapter we will discuss some dubious early sidelines which, however, can be used as a blitz weapon against you. } 
1.e4  e5  
2.Nf3  d6  { This is rather passive and allows White to gain a space advantage. } 
3.d4  {[%csl Re5]} {[%cal Gd4e5]} { The most dynamic approach. Please, note that it is important to play it immediately instead of [Bc4] since in most cases we are going to castle long as quickly as possible. Our priority is to develop queenside pieces. } exd4  
