6.e5 $1 {[%cal Be5f6]} {[%cal Bd4d8]} {[%csl Rf6]} Nc6  
7.Bb5 $1 { Pinning the knight and forcing Black to enter a worse endgame. } dxe5  
8.Qxd8+  Kxd8  
9.Bxc6  bxc6  
10.Nxe5  {[%cal Be5f7]} {[%cal Be5c6]} Ke8  
11.Bd2 $14 {[%cal Be1c1]} ( 11. Bd2 { Followed by } 11...-- 12.O-O-O { with a very pleasant edge due to a better pawn structure and the fact that Black has lost the right to castle. } ) ( { Taking on } 11.Nxc6 { instead would have been a mistake because of } 11...Bb7 { and we lose our pawn on [g2]. } )  *

