6.Qd2  b5  { Black has made 5 out of 6 starting moves with the pawns! I feel like opening the position should give White advantage. We have a lead in development, so playing aggressively makes sense. } 
7.h5 $5 { Provoking [g5]. } g5  
8.f4 $5 { Opening the position. } gxf4  
9.Bxf4  Nf6  
10.a3  {[%csl Rb4]} { Preventing [b5]-[b4]. } Bb7  {[%cal Gb7e4]} {[%cal Gf6e4]} {[%csl Re4]} 
