7.e5 $16 {[%cal Bd1f3]} {[%cal Gf3f7]} {[%cal Gf3a8]} {[%csl Ra8]} {[%csl Rf7]} { Threatening 8...-- 9.Qf3 double-attacking the a8-rook and the f7-pawn! Also, another idea is to push 9.e6 forcing some concessions. } Nh6  { Another way to protect the [f7]-pawn. Now we need to play... } 
8.e6 $1 { Damaging Black's pawn structure, making the [g6]-pawn vulnerable. } Bxe6  
